# Build artifacts
bin/
/docker-update
/hmi-update

# Test infrastructure
e2e/
*.test
coverage.out

# Planning + docs
# Exclude specific operator/dev docs at the build-context root rather than
# globbing `*.md` everywhere — the global glob is one careless `//go:embed
# *.md` away from a silent build (markdown file embedded as empty). Anchor
# each pattern to `/` so a future internal package can ship a `doc.md`
# without surprises. See Phase 7 REVIEW WR-04.
.planning/
/README.md
/API.md
/RELEASING.md
/SMOKE.md
/CLAUDE.md
/hmi-update-brief.md

# Editor / OS
.vscode/
.idea/
.DS_Store

# Git
.git/
.gitignore
.gitattributes

# CI configs
.github/

# Node build leftovers — ui-builder stage runs its own npm ci
ui/node_modules/
ui/dist/
# NOTE: internal/api/dist is intentionally NOT excluded — the ui-builder
# stage rebuilds it inside the image, but if a developer pre-built it
# locally we want the host context to upload the freshly-built version
# too (defensive). It's tiny (~1 MB) so the upload cost is negligible.
